column1: You shouldn't have to have legislation to enforce what is already law. #COVID19 #coronavirus

The Stanford University model said Florida would have 465,000 #COVID19 hospitalizations by April 24th FL has 2000 The models are WRONG. Was this intentional missinformation and MSM propaganda? #coronavirus

Is there any actually legal basis to force people to stay at home? the government can order quarantine for specific individuals infected with certain diseases. I don't think they can trample on the Constitutional rights of the whole country. #COVID19 #coronavirus
